### ===== ERP 完整业务流程 =====

### 1. 登录拿 token
# @name login
POST http://localhost:8080/api/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "admin123"
}

### 2. 看我的菜单
GET http://localhost:8080/api/menus/me
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.data.token}}

### 3. 看物料列表
GET http://localhost:8080/api/business/material/page?page=1&size=10
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.data.token}}

### 4. 看仓库列表
GET http://localhost:8080/api/business/warehouse
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.data.token}}

### 5. 创建采购单：iPhone 10 个，单价 4500
# @name createPur
POST http://localhost:8080/api/business/purchase
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.data.token}}

{
  "supplierName": "苹果供应商",
  "warehouseId": 1,
  "remark": "12 月备货",
  "items": [
    {"materialId": 1, "quantity": 10, "price": 4500}
  ]
}

### 6. 审核采购单
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/business/purchase/{{createPur.response.body.data}}/approve
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.data.token}}

### 7. 入库
POST http://localhost:8080/api/business/purchase/{{createPur.response.body.data}}/inbound
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.data.token}}

### 8. 查库存：应该看到 iPhone 库存 10
GET http://localhost:8080/api/business/stock?materialId=1
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.data.token}}

### 9. 创建销售单：iPhone 卖 3 个，单价 5999
# @name createSal
POST http://localhost:8080/api/business/sale
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.data.token}}

{
  "customerName": "门店 A",
  "warehouseId": 1,
  "items": [
    {"materialId": 1, "quantity": 3, "price": 5999}
  ]
}

### 10. 审核销售单
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/business/sale/{{createSal.response.body.data}}/approve
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.data.token}}

### 11. 出库
POST http://localhost:8080/api/business/sale/{{createSal.response.body.data}}/outbound
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.data.token}}

### 12. 查库存：应该剩 7
GET http://localhost:8080/api/business/stock?materialId=1
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.data.token}}

### 13. 查流水：应该有 2 条 (+10 入库, -3 出库)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/business/stock/1/logs
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.data.token}}

### 14. 故意超卖：销售 100 个 → 应该返回库存不足
POST http://localhost:8080/api/business/sale
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.data.token}}

{
  "customerName": "想吃霸王餐",
  "warehouseId": 1,
  "items": [{"materialId": 1, "quantity": 100, "price": 5999}]
}

# 接下来需要审核 + 出库才会真实尝试扣减
# 走 9-11 三步，第 11 步会回滚并返回 STOCK_INSUFFICIENT

### 15. 看操作日志
GET http://localhost:8080/api/users
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.data.token}}
# 注：操作日志在 sys_operation_log 表里，自己用 SQL 看
